      "url": "https://app.guesty.com/api/pm-websites-backend/listings?minOccupancy=1&fields=_id+title+roomType+beds+timezone+publicDescription+picture+address+accommodates+bedrooms+bathrooms+propertyType+prices+reviews+nightlyRates+totalPrice+isRecommended",
      "status": 200,
      "preview": "{\"results\":[{\"_id\":\"69fb33d01cd9700014a4b376\",\"title\":\"Modern 2BR Steps to Beach by HolyGuest\",\"roomType\":\"Entire home/apt\",\"beds\":3,\"timezone\":\"Asia/Jerusalem\",\"publicDescription\":{\"summary\":\"Set on Trumpeldor Street just steps from the beach, this bright 2-bedroom apartment offers a relaxed and modern stay for up to 5 guests. With its sea view, private balcony, and fully renovated design, it’s the perfect spot to enjoy Tel Aviv’s coastal lifestyle in comfort and style.\",\"space\":\"A bright, easygoing seaside home 🌊\\n\\nLocated on the 4th floor of a well-kept building, this freshly renovated apartment blends modern design with a relaxed coastal vibe. Natural light, sea breeze, and clean interiors set the tone for your stay.\\n\\nWake up, open the balcony doors, and enjoy the sea view right from your living space.\\n\\n✨ Inside the apartment:\\n• 🌅 Private balcony with open sea view\\n• Spacious, light-filled living area\\n• 🛏️ 2 comfortable bedrooms for up to 5 guests\\n• 🚿 1 modern bathroom\\n• 🍳 Fully equipped kitchen with sleek finishes\\n• 🪞 Fresh, minimalist renovation throughout\\n\\n📍 The location:\\nRight on Trumpeldor, you’re a few steps from the beach and surrounded by cafés, bakeries, and the best of Tel Aviv’s seaside energy.\\n\\n🏢 Building:\\n• 4th floor\\n• Elevator in the building\\n\\n🔐 Security:\\n• Miklat (secured shelter) available in the building\\n\\n🌆 Good to know:\\nThe area is central and lively, with the natural energy of the city and occasional urban noise.\\n\\n💙 What makes it special:\\n• True sea view from the balcony\\n• Clean, modern, fully renovated feel\\n• Walkable beach lifestyle\\n• Perfect base for families or small groups\\n\\n🚗 Parking:\\nNo private parking. Several public parking solutions are available nearby within walking distance.\",\"access\":\"Guests have full access to the apartment.\\n\\nYou’ll also have access to the HolyGuest app with curated local recommendations, digital guidebooks, and optional services like food delivery and Shabbat meals."
    },
